Home > Music > Adrien Broner Enters Boxing Arena With Kodak Black Adrien Broner Enters Boxing Arena With Kodak Black 0 0   10:00am Kodak Black escorted Adrien Broner to the ring last Saturday night. 
Adrien Broner prevailed in his boxing match last night against Adrian Granados by 10-round split decision. Before the fight, which took place in Broner's hometown Cincinnati, he walked out to the ring Kodak Black by his side. 
Broner sported a Kodak Black-style ski mask, a gold grill, and a gold and black tunic with the words ABOUT BILLIONS blazoned across the chest. Kodak wore one of Broner's belts over his right shoulder and rapped into a mic as they stepped out into the arena. 
Broner's victory advanced his record to 33-2. Kodak's new music video "Tunnel Vision" has garnered six million views in three days. He is scheduled to join Future, Migos , and Tory Lanez on the "Nobody Safe" tour this spring.   10:00am 1 View
